    <description>The AK-103 assault rifle is a derivative of the AK-74M chambered for the 7.62×39mm M43 round, similar to the older AKM. The AK-103 can be fitted with a variety of sights, including night vision and telescopic sights, plus a knife-bayonet or a grenade launcher. 
	
It uses plastic components where possible instead of wood or metal, with such components being the pistol grip, handguards and stock.</description>
